cu.explanation_en: Setting hw_log_level to an invalid value 'invalid_hw' will cause hardware logging configuration errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting pusch_AntennaPorts to a negative value -1 will cause antenna configuration validation errors as it expects a positive integer.
du.explanation_zh: 將 pusch_AntennaPorts 設定為負值 -1 會導致天線配置驗證錯誤，因為它期望正整數。
